N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1ยง 8.3 - Identification stamp or stencil

State Regulations

The identification stamp or stencil shall include the
type of cheese to be marked, namely: cheddar cheese, washed curd cheese, or
colby cheese and shall include a plant identification number to be assigned by
the commissioner. Notes
